<div id='root'><div class='wrap'>
  <div class='eye'>The Problem</div>
  <h1>1,000 timesheets a month.<br><em>All processed by hand.</em></h1>
  <p class='sub'>OPG receives timesheets from clients in 25 different formats &mdash; PDF, Excel, Word, JPEG, email, paper. Every single one is manually read, interpreted, and entered into Recman by the operations team. The import window is three days. Any missing data means additional manual research before entry can proceed.</p>
  <div class='kpi-grid'>
    <div class='kpi'><div class='kpi-n'>1,000+</div><div class='kpi-l'>timesheets processed manually every month</div><div class='kpi-s'>25 different client formats</div></div>
