    <div class='kpi'><div class='kpi-n'>237</div><div class='kpi-l'>employer certificates issued in March 2026 alone</div><div class='kpi-s'>Up to 50 minutes each, manual</div></div>
    <div class='kpi'><div class='kpi-n'>1,000+</div><div class='kpi-l'>timesheet entries processed manually every single month across the ops team</div><div class='kpi-s'>All typed into Recman by hand</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class='cols'>
    <div class='card'>
      <div class='card-eye'>Timesheet problem</div>
      <div class='card-title'>25 formats. One manual process. Three days to do it all.</div>
      <div class='prob-list'>
        <div class='prob-item'><div class='prob-dot'></div>Every client sends timesheets differently &mdash; no standard format, no standard channel</div>
        <div class='prob-item'><div class='prob-dot'></div>Missing fields require manual research across the employee contract and collective agreement before entry can proceed</div>
        <div class='prob-item'><div class='prob-dot'></div>The ops team has three days to process everything &mdash; the 2nd to the 5th of every month. Any delay or unclear file slows the whole process down</div>
        <div class='prob-item'><div class='prob-dot'></div>Every missing field requires manual research across contracts and collective agreements before the entry can proceed</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class='card'>
      <div class='card-eye'>Employer certificate problem</div>
      <div class='card-title'>An indefinite legal obligation. Fully manual. No end date.</div>
      <div class='prob-list'>
        <div class='prob-item'><div class='prob-dot'></div>OPG must produce employer certificates for any consultant who has ever worked for the group &mdash; upon request, with no time limit</div>
        <div class='prob-item'><div class='prob-dot'></div>Each certificate requires data from two separate systems: Recman for employment history, Visma Spiris for final salary</div>
        <div class='prob-item'><div class='prob-dot'></div>One certificate takes up to 50 minutes of manual assembly</div>
        <div class='prob-item'><div class='prob-dot'></div>237 certificates in March alone. The volume only grows as the group does</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
