<div id='root'><div class='wrap'>
  <div class='eye'>Before We Start</div>
  <h1>What we need from OPG<br><em>before April 14th.</em></h1>
  <p class='sub'>None of these are blockers to beginning the Foundation phase. They affect Foundation + Intelligence and Full Suite estimates. The two marked HIGH are on the critical path &mdash; the sooner we have them, the sooner we can give accurate numbers.</p>
  <div class='dep-grid'>
    <div class='dep'>
      <div class='dep-priority high'>HIGH</div>
      <div class='dep-main'><div class='dep-owner'>Andreas Nordlund</div><div class='dep-title'>Recman API documentation</div><div class='dep-body'>Priority endpoints: employee profile, job by date, collective agreement lookup, contracted hours. If key endpoints are missing, the gap-fill approach changes significantly.</div></div>
      <div class='dep-impact'><div class='dep-impact-text'><strong>Without this:</strong> Foundation + Intelligence cannot be accurately scoped or priced. This is the single most important input before the meeting.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class='dep'>
      <div class='dep-priority high'>HIGH</div>
      <div class='dep-main'><div class='dep-owner'>Andreas Nordlund</div><div class='dep-title'>Visma Spiris API access confirmed</div><div class='dep-body'>Salary data for employer certificates lives here. If there is no API, Full Suite uses a scheduled export instead &mdash; workable but adds a step and changes the timeline.</div></div>
      <div class='dep-impact'><div class='dep-impact-text'><strong>Without this:</strong> Full Suite cannot be fully scoped or priced.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class='dep'>
      <div class='dep-priority med'>MED</div>
      <div class='dep-main'><div class='dep-owner'>Rickard Fornes + ops team</div><div class='dep-title'>Number of active collective agreements</div><div class='dep-body'>How many distinct kollektivavtal are active across OPG&apos;s jobs? Each agreement needs its own rule-set in the gap-fill engine. More agreements = more build time.</div></div>
      <div class='dep-impact'><div class='dep-impact-text'><strong>Without this:</strong> Foundation + Intelligence estimate will carry a wider range until confirmed.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class='dep'>
      <div class='dep-priority med'>MED</div>
      <div class='dep-main'><div class='dep-owner'>Ops team</div><div class='dep-title'>Missing timesheet rate</div><div class='dep-body'>What percentage of the 1,000 monthly timesheets arrive with missing start/end/break data? If above 20%, the gap-fill agent becomes critical path and accuracy is the primary KPI.</div></div>
      <div class='dep-impact'><div class='dep-impact-text'><strong>Without this:</strong> Hard to size Foundation + Intelligence accurately or set realistic KPIs for the pilot.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div></div>
